Meet <b>davapink</b>, our latest Citizen of the Week. <br><br>She lives at <a href="http://millsberry.com/home/?user=davapink"><a href='/home/?user=davapink'>34465-B Rosewood Road</a> in Ravenwood</a> and has been a citizen since September 17, 2007!<br><br>Davapink's very caring, generous, and friendly. Her interests include karate, more karate, and helping people learn...karate! This could explain the high score she earned on the Arcade's Black Belt Karate game! Davapink's also very passionate about computers, acting, and music. Her favorite colors are black, violet, and magenta. In fact, she thinks magenta should be the color of the highest belt in karate since it's such a special hue! <br><br>As for davapink's abode, the sprawling home is very impressive. And it seems like she's adding more rooms and yards to it every day! Davapink has collected 26 trophies since she's been in town, and they shine beneath their very own spotlight in her home. In her spare time, davapink likes to hang out at her best friend's house and trade clothes. This said: If you want to impress her, think about surprising her with a disc of disco tunes! </div>
